{
  "stem": "4753.10",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other one we did that-- some man from the men barracks, what was very far away from us-- I don't know where-- came to cut off-- off squared piece of earth, and we had to carry it to the SS men barracks, because they loved flowers.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they wanted to have a garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We sat the problem was that we couldn't straighten up as we were cutting this piece of earth, because it was very, very heavy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you dropped it, you were lucky if you were not shot, but you definitely were punished.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beaten or not getting your bread or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I cannot give you a-- a straight answer because, first of all, we didn't think about how I will cope with it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naturally, we coped with it because we had no other choice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Evening, when we finally huddled together and wanted to go to sleep, we naturally talked about all the things what was going through our mind.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We talked about home and about our parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We described exactly every detail about them and our sisters and brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We cooked what we never did at home, but, now we all cooked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We talked about food, because we were hungry nonstop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in wintertime, we were terrible cold and freezing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were just talking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe that was the only way we coped with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I cannot think any other way [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we could do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Auschwitz-- in Auschwitz dream?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In concentration camps-- dreams, we had a million.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in Braunschweig-- that was the city where we had to clean the main road.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were taken to Braunschweig from Auschwitz through Bergen-Belsen to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to clean the main road.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
